---
3md: 1.0
axis: depth
view: blend
legend: "#=●"
billboard: true
category: Creative
title: CorvidLabs Mark in 3D
note: the CorvidLabs logo as a voxel sculpture - a sphere head, a cone beak, a carved eye. Open in blend and drag to orbit.
---
The CorvidLabs mark, lifted off the page. Each plane is one depth slice; blend
them and the raven head, beak, and eye fuse into a small 3D logo you can spin.

